(155, 4, '2013-02-23 20:31:20', '2013-02-23 20:31:20', 'After a very successful trip, we decided it would be nice to share our experience with our fans. What is <strong>PROJECT MVMNT</strong>? Well, it’s a new segment of PROJECT, the world’s most preeminent contemporary fashion trade event, which will serve as an area dedicated to the community and businesses driving the growth of youth culture. We were very happy to be a part of the trend setter movement within the skate and street world. <strong>PROJECT MVMNT  </strong>was held at the Mandalay Bay Convention center in Las Vegas. Here''s some pictures of our experience at <strong>PROJECT MVMNT[gallery ids="188,189,157,170,168,167,165,185,160,159,175,180,176,178,163,171,184"]\r\n\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFeb 19-21 2013.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'PROJECT MVMNT / MAGIC', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'project-mvmnt-magic', '', '', '2013-02-23 20:49:04', '2013-02-23 20:49:04', '', 0, 'http://www.jordancraig.net/updates/?p=155', 0, 'post', '', 1),
